**Append** to `.agent/frontend-improvement-agent.log`:

```
---
## Session [N] — [YYYY-MM-DD]
**Category**: P[0-6] — [name]
**Files changed**: [list]
**Summary**: [1-2 sentences]
**Pattern files used**: [which patterns/ files were read]
