**Verification**: typecheck [pass/fail] | lint [pass/fail] | tests [pass/fail] | build [pass/fail]
**Git**: branch [name] | commit [short SHA or "n/a"] | push [ok / failed: reason]

### NEXT_SESSION_QUEUE
1. [P-level] [description] — [file/component]
2. [P-level] [description] — [file/component]
3. [P-level] [description] — [file/component]
